unittitle_ssm: Leonard Larsen Papers
abstract_ssm: The Leonard Larsen Papers, dating from 1942 to 1945, chronicle the Larsen family during World War II on the home front and abroad. The majority of the collection is letters between Leonard Larsen and his wife, Helen.
heading_ssm: Leonard Larsen Papers
